data.description: Feast your eyes on this immaculate, meticulously maintained 5 bedroom 4 bathroom home. Nestled in the coveted River Walk Farm subdivision, this spacious traditional 2 story home, features a 3 car garage, level private backyard with pergola and jacuzzi. Inside the floorplan is ABSOLUTELY AMAZING - not a detail was spared in this layout! This home was made for entertaining friends and family alike. The main level welcomes you into a 2 story foyer and separate office/living room beautifully decorated and inviting just the same. Multiples spaces for dining as it boasts both a formal dining room, as well as an eat-in kitchen with views to the fireside family room. A bedroom, full bathroom, and laundry room complete the main level. Upstairs features a loft/2nd living room, 4 secondary bedrooms and 3 additional bathrooms including the Owner's Suite w/ sitting room, tray ceiling, double vanity with separate tub and shower.  Community boasts swim, tennis, soccer, basketball courts, and playground! Look no further, there is no home sweeter this this one!
